type: collection
name: kaijo/pfsense-crowdsec-collection-suite
description: >
  Comprehensive CrowdSec Collection Suite for pfSense CE and pfSense Plus.
  Includes pfSense-specific SSH parsers (RFC3164/RFC5424) and SSH security
  scenarios with full hubtest validation. Designed for FreeBSD/OpenSSH log
  variants used by pfSense.

author: kaijo
license: MIT
version: 0.1.6

tags:
  - pfSense
  - FreeBSD
  - SSH
  - Security
  - Firewall
  - CrowdSec

labels:
  platform: pfSense
  suite: true
